summary: AN ORDINANCE repealing Seattle Municipal Code Chapters 6.06, 6.26, 6.34, 6.52, and 6.210 (Ordinance 48022 Sections 331-331.8; 267-270; Sections 302-305; and Sections 206-209; and a portion of Ordinance 108934 respectively) to end the licensing and regulation of bail bondsmen, going out of business or closing-out sales; locksmiths; side sewer contractors; and for-hire vehicles other than taxicabs.
